### Get all reactions for the test run
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/reactions

### Get specific reaction details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/reactions/building-comfort

### Start the reaction handler (if not auto-started)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/reactions/building-comfort/start

### Stop the reaction handler
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/reactions/building-comfort/stop

### Pause the reaction handler
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/reactions/building-comfort/pause

### Resume the reaction handler
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/reactions/building-comfort/resume